genresAdvancedInfo.name: viet instrumental
genresAdvancedInfo.description: This genre of music is characterized by its use of traditional Vietnamese instruments such as the đàn tranh, đàn bầu, and đàn nguyệt. The music is often soothing and melodic, with a focus on creating a peaceful and meditative atmosphere.
